作为一个程序员，这里自然少不了关于计算机相关技术的分享。.message: As a programmer, it's natural for there to be a sharing of computer-related technologies here.

编程、网络、硬件……各种类型的分享都可能会出现。我也可能分享我自己开发的一些项目.message: Programming, networking, hardware... various types of shares might occur. I may also share some projects that I have developed, as well as the technologies used and insights gained during the development process.

欢迎关注我的 Github，以获取更多我开发的项目：.message: Feel free to follow my Github for more projects I have developed:

摄影是我的主要业余爱好之一。.message: Photography is one of my main hobbies.

我会不定期挑选一些我拍摄的照片，并分享背后拍摄的故事和后期心得。另外，我也可能会.message: From time to time, I select some of the photos I've taken and share the stories behind them, as well as insights from post-processing. Additionally, I might introduce some basic principles and techniques related to photography.

查询所有关于摄影的文章。.message: to show all articles about photography.

此外，也欢迎关注我的 Flickr 或订阅我的 Telegram 频道，以获取更.message: Furthermore, you're welcome to follow my Flickr or subscribe to my Telegram channel to see more of my photographs:

除了一些正经的文章，我也会在这里发表一些我自己的碎碎念。.message: In addition to some serious articles, I will also share some of my random thoughts here.

它们可能是我的突发奇想，也可能是我的某些奇怪的感悟。.message: They might be my sudden whims, or some of my strange epiphanies.

ACM/ICPC WF 大牛，作为他的同事只能瑟瑟发抖并仰慕.message: ACM/ICPC WF genius, as his colleague can only tremble and admire

朋友就像口袋里的硬币，不需要满满当当，只求质优价钱高。.message: Friends are like coins in your pocket, they don't need to be full, just high quality and valuable.

真正的朋友会在你忘记携带笑面具时，递给你一张次日可用的笑容优惠券。.message: A true friend will hand you a smile coupon that can be used the next day when you forget to bring your smile mask.

与朋友相处，就像用手机，信号不好时不是换朋友，而是换个好位置。.message: Getting along with friends is like using a cellphone. When the signal is weak, you don't change friends, you just find a better spot.

论偷懒的共犯，一位懂事的朋友胜过一打勤快的助手。.message: A responsible friend is better than a dozen diligent assistants when it comes to being lazy partners.

好友像是生活的调料包，少了他们，即使是五星大餐也变得索然无味。.message: Friends are like seasoning packets in life, without them, even a five-star meal becomes tasteless.

朋友就像是双重馅饼：一层是欢笑，另一层是在你开心忘形时偷偷录视频的家伙。.message: Friends are like double-layered pies: one layer is laughter, and the other layer is the person who secretly records videos of you when you're happy and carefree.

好友之间的对话就像是密码锁，别人听着就像是摩斯电码。.message: Conversations between friends are like a combination lock, sounding like Morse code to others.

一个真正的朋友会在你愚蠢行为的第一排给你鼓掌，并准备好第一个不合时宜的玩笑。.message: A true friend will clap for you in the front row of your foolish behavior and be ready with the first inappropriate joke.

朋友是那个知道你所有缺点，但还是坚决不肯公开拍卖这些信息的人。.message: A friend is someone who knows all your flaws but still refuses to publicly auction off that information.

朋友就像是生活中的弹出广告，你不记得订阅了他们，但他们总是及时出现。.message: Friends are like pop-up ads in life, you don't remember subscribing to them, but they always appear on time.

一起在厨房制造混乱和烹饪灾难，是友谊的不成文规定。.message: Creating chaos and cooking disasters together in the kitchen is an unwritten rule of friendship.

朋友会在你决定剪个新发型后，诚实地告诉你，你现在看起来像一只逃跑的羊。.message: A friend will honestly tell you that you look like a runaway sheep when you decide to get a new hairstyle.

朋友就像彩虹，当你的生活被暴风雨弄得一团糟时，他们会出现并画出一道笑脸。.message: Friends are like rainbows, they appear and draw a smiley face when your life is in chaos due to a storm.

拥有一个朋友就像拥有一个活生生的备忘录，时刻提醒你过去所有糗事的细节。.message: Having a friend is like having a living memo, constantly reminding you of all the embarrassing details from the past.

与朋友共饮一杯，哪怕是难喝的自制酒，也胜过独自享用世界上最好的美酒。.message: Sharing a drink with a friend, even if it's a poorly made homemade one, is better than enjoying the best wine in the world alone.

朋友是那种你可以在任何无聊的活动中一起无聊的人，就连排队等公交都变得好玩。.message: Friends are the kind of people you can be bored together with in any boring activity, even waiting in line for a bus becomes fun.

朋友不是互相吹捧的镜子，而是那种能一起互相吐槽对方颜值的搭档。.message: Friends are not mirrors that flatter each other, but partners who can mock each other's appearance together.

在我无能为力时给我电影票的朋友，比给我励志名言的人要好得多。.message: A friend who gives me a movie ticket when I feel helpless is much better than someone who gives me inspirational quotes.

朋友不会让你做傻事……至少不会让你单独去做傻事。.message: Friends won't let you do stupid things... at least not alone.

朋友是会在你穿新鞋的时候，用力踩一脚，然后满脸无辜地说“哦，不好意思，我没看见”.message: A friend is someone who will step on your new shoes with force and then innocently say, 'Oh, sorry, I didn't see them.'

从中学到大学的同学，SJTU 辩论队里那些能说会道的人之一 :P.message: Classmates from middle school to university, one of those eloquent people in the SJTU Debate Team :P

认识许久的网友，持续专注于 Qt 相关领域.message: A longtime online friend who continues to focus on the field of Qt

偶然搜索到的博客，热爱软件技术的医生维护的跨领域知识库.message: A blog discovered by chance, maintained by a doctor who loves software technology, serving as a cross-disciplinary knowledge base.

同样在 2023 年重启了自己博客的网友，相识于少数派.message: A netizen who also restarted their blog in 2023, met through the community of SSPAI.
